101.title: Christina Milian
101.plot: Host Brody Jenner, comedian Stevie Ryan, and sex and relationship therapist Dr. Mike Dow offer a fresh take on tackling life's biggest mystery... sex and intimacy, all through a celebrity and pop culture lens in this comedic podcast talk show. The premiere episode features guest Christina Milian.

imdb.plot outline: You may know reality TV star Brody Jenner from such hit shows as "Keeping up with the Kardashians" and "The Hills," but you've never seen him like this. In the new series, "Sex with Brody," Brody Jenner takes viewers on an in-depth exploration of the most provocative subject of all: sex. Joining Jenner are relationship therapist Dr. Mike Dow and actress Stevie Ryan, as well as weekly celebrity guests. Together, they will delve into questions about sex and intimacy that everyone wants answers to, as well as assist callers with issues in their sex lives.
